</div>
<div>
<p>　　<measure quantity="5" unit="months">
<num value="5">五</num>月</measure>
<num value="53">丙辰</num>
<pc>，</pc>以旱<pc>，</pc>決中外系囚<pc>。</pc>除茶鹽賞錢<pc>。</pc>有司上<pc>《</pc>
